OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLonger lorries to be       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fallowed on Britain's roads 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has approved the use of 
OL,6, longer lorries on British roads, saying
OL,7, it will make businesses more efficient 
OL,8, and cut emissions.                     
OL,10,FThe industry welcome the move, saying  
OL,11,Fit would mean more goods could be      
OL,12,Ftransported by fewer vehicles.         
OL,14,FOne campaign group warned the larger   
OL,15,Ftail swing, meaning their rear end     
OL,16,Fcovers a bigger area when turning could
OL,17,Fput pedestrians and cyclists at risk.  
OL,19,FMinisters said the lorries, which have 
OL,20,Fbeen trialled since 2011, are safe.    
